  "title": "Operations Manager for Indian restaurant",
  "description": "<p>1. Day to day Operations and management for 3 outlets (4th outlet expansion is in-progress )  </p><p>2. Should be ready for extended hours (Morning 5 AM to 11 PM) with multiple small breaks<br /><br />3. Fluent in English/Tamil/Mandarin/Malay (atleast 2 combinations Mandatory) to handle customer service</p><p>4. Food safety course from SFA is mandatory</p><p>5. Knowledge in Microsoft word and Excel (Certification will be added advantage)</p><p>6. Nutrition certificate will be added advantage</p><p>7. Billing and Accounts needs to be co-ordinated with Accounts/Auditing team on weekly basis.</p><p>8. Human resources management. Staff attendance, entry and exit timing management in software system. </p><p>9. Maintain inventory and stocks (Supplier management)</p><p>10. Fixing the menu for the day and arranging the stocks accordingly in advance</p><p>11. Create/Handle Social media marketing / Digital marketing<br /><br />12. Ready to handle different timings and need to handle all the outlet queries and shifts</p><p>13. Monthly 2 days off based on work load staff availability.</p><p>14. Maintain high standards of hygiene</p><p>15. Catering management, Packaging and delivery should be handled in efficient way to maintain the cost.</p>",
